=== Noodle dishes ===
[[Image:CantoneseWontonnoodle.jpg|thumb|right|[[Wonton noodle]]s]]

Noodles are served either in soup broth or fried. These are available as home-cooked meals, on [[dim sum]] side menus, or as street food at [[dai pai dong]]s, where they can be served with a variety of toppings such as [[fish ball]]s, [[beef ball]]s, or [[fish slice]]s.

