===Siu mei===
{{main|Siu mei}}
[[Image:HKloumei.jpg|thumb|upright|[[Siu mei]] and [[Lou mei]] [[charcuterie]]]]

''[[Siu mei]]'' ({{zh|s=烧味|t=燒味|p=shāo wèi|j=siu1 mei6}}) is essentially the Chinese [[rotisserie]] style of cooking. Unlike most other Cantonese dishes, siu mei consists of meat only, with no vegetables.

