===Siu laap===
[[Image:CantoneseSiuLaapStore.jpg|thumb|right|Siu laap store front]]

All Cantonese-style cooked meats, including [[siu mei]], [[lou mei]] and preserved meat can be classified as '''siu laap''' ({{zh|s=烧腊|t=燒臘|p=shāo là|j=siu1 laap6}}). ''Siu laap'' also includes dishes such as:

