===Dessert===
[[Image:CantoneseHybridRedbeansoup.jpg|thumb|right|Hybrid [[red bean soup]] with [[taro]]]]

After the evening meal, most Cantonese restaurants offer [[tong sui]] ({{zh|s=糖水|t=糖水|p=táng shuǐ|j=tong4 seoi2|l=sugar water}}), a sweet soup. Many varieties of tong sui are also found in other Chinese cuisines. Some desserts are traditional, while others are recent innovations. The more expensive restaurants usually offer their specialty desserts.

